{"tid":223872,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無低學歷30歲先轉行既經驗可以分享？","createTime":"2017-04-30T15:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T14:47:36.000Z","uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10b8f4fadd6197e7b56f079f68172518dc1b1ede","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"情況係未讀完中五就退學<br />\n加加埋埋做左7-8年sales,時間長收入唔穩定又無技術<br />\n今年3張野了，想學返一技之長<br />\nvtc個學徒計劃好唔好？<br />\n定去讀返個毅進先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27d161e061051fea47ce48cc3baef9a8c400dbf","tid":223872,"uid":60153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08776449b54f0867949a8332cee1d2390d9e0173","tid":223872,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"讀書啦"},{"pid":"ae62945dcd628ea9700c0db28855b1293fec853e","tid":223872,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"政府工不二之選"},{"pid":"5a5e82c4a1108f18440b48a58db95b61872930f0","tid":223872,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"試下海關"},{"pid":"17653a4d20eb33c0f25ce503d07f364683f4cc32","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀完毅進--&gt;紀律部隊</blockquote><br />\n唔想做差佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大近視做唔倒消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返入境海關救護？"},{"pid":"3b1fe5ef11f72e2b1055c8692a82328c41686e43","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀書啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVTC學徒有無用？半工讀四年有張滿師紙同文憑<br />\n其實有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b3fa0d1abe414cbe2910db1d91bda6d70faa46","tid":223872,"uid":60153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90706c902a727e831b459847347d6aa4a98a8641","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府工不二之選</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左郵差我學歷最多只能做二級工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但郵差好似好多高學歷既人apply"},{"pid":"87ecdfae2260f0881f44d8b8787b7910f454a5c8","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀完毅進--&gt;紀律部隊</blockquote><br />\n唔想做差佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大近視做唔倒消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返入境海關救護？</blockquote><br />\n除左差佬外其他都唔洗諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解？因為其他部隊門檻高好多？"},{"pid":"7a5145915191388fa31d97d0ae38a254c23a34ab","tid":223872,"uid":60858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讀完毅進--&gt;紀律部隊</blockquote><br />\n唔想做差佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大近視做唔倒消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返入境海關救護？</blockquote><br />\n大把高學歷嘅想考入境海關，讀完偽進都未必入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中五畢業都無，除咗出賣勞力同sales，都應該無乜可以揀了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb91433a57eb47878db786041bef185e007a9e1","tid":223872,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"30歲有紀律部隊收咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ce368c158a77fe50cab88ede25365b92ab3f91","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀完毅進--&gt;紀律部隊</blockquote><br />\n唔想做差佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大近視做唔倒消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得返入境海關救護？</blockquote><br />\n大把高學歷嘅想考入境海關，讀完偽進都未必入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中五畢業都無，除咗出賣勞力同sales，都應該無乜可以揀了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我唔介意勞動，但勞力一樣可以被輕易取代<br />\n所以諗住想轉試下行做技工，但又無從入手"},{"pid":"e14d966d98e08b31a1f0839a43385477e2007a48","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>30歲有紀律部隊收咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗都難，又唔係有咩過人之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059ce7f3d940aefaf6775c0415c9b3b57518a76e","tid":223872,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:28:34.000Z","msg":"紀律部隊你估咁易入咩"},{"pid":"87faa62aba2e2e3c02dca82a3f482453ee583665","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紀律部隊你估咁易入咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知，自問條件唔及人<br />\n個個都想做既工邊夠人爭<br />\n所以傾向比較人手短缺既行業<br />\n睇見幾多報導講未來十年技工退休潮機會多<br />\n話滿師出黎做個師傅穩袋2皮幾<br />\n不過我見勞工處請維修師傅5年經驗有A牌都係得16,17k<br />\n都唔知係咪報紙佬做新聞"},{"pid":"b31d7710a0e3f79c3dd81ccb169896aa106c21d8","tid":223872,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>紀律部隊你估咁易入咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知，自問條件唔及人<br />\n個個都想做既工邊夠人爭<br />\n所以傾向比較人手短缺既行業<br />\n睇見幾多報導講未來十年技工退休潮機會多<br />\n話滿師出黎做個師傅穩袋2皮幾<br />\n不過我見勞工處請維修師傅5年經驗有A牌都係得16,17k<br />\n都唔知係咪報紙佬做新聞</blockquote><br />\n去CIC學返一門手藝"},{"pid":"786ac2d2043ac24b41b50660c9ab497f83f6e984","tid":223872,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>政府工不二之選</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左郵差我學歷最多只能做二級工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但郵差好似好多高學歷既人apply</blockquote><br />\n流失太多,<br />\n郵差而家唔收高學歷"},{"pid":"6ee6bedf6b47d4912bd2f97c29734bacf4128a56","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>政府工不二之選</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左郵差我學歷最多只能做二級工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但郵差好似好多高學歷既人apply</blockquote><br />\n流失太多,<br />\n郵差而家唔收高學歷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上星期Apply左，平常心一試<br />\n但唔想守株待兔，諗緊仲有咩路可行"},{"pid":"68b89e70cbda5f539418194a3d967e617433b7a7","tid":223872,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>30歲有紀律部隊收咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗都難，又唔係有咩過人之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把30入紀律部隊啦"},{"pid":"6d5714a39f8a8a133ea6fda22e1305062a39d718","tid":223872,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>紀律部隊你估咁易入咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知，自問條件唔及人<br />\n個個都想做既工邊夠人爭<br />\n所以傾向比較人手短缺既行業<br />\n睇見幾多報導講未來十年技工退休潮機會多<br />\n話滿師出黎做個師傅穩袋2皮幾<br />\n不過我見勞工處請維修師傅5年經驗有A牌都係得16,17k<br />\n都唔知係咪報紙佬做新聞</blockquote><br />\n勞工處專出賤價請人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇文員有7千蚊都知咩事啦"},{"pid":"da551e17bff58376dc7d8bc9f696c81dd9538bd3","tid":223872,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:01:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88c48a2ac58f5186f4f731b66c74ee52fab2f38c","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>30歲有紀律部隊收咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗都難，又唔係有咩過人之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把30入紀律部隊啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要補返個毅進，讀埋出黎都差唔多32<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0aeaf3a051bc71169318ea4b5440c7c666d270","tid":223872,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:20:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>nursing</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要由中四讀到degree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f1dcbccdcec851c79bba0b76abeb659c68312c","tid":223872,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>紀律部隊你估咁易入咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知，自問條件唔及人<br />\n個個都想做既工邊夠人爭<br />\n所以傾向比較人手短缺既行業<br />\n睇見幾多報導講未來十年技工退休潮機會多<br />\n話滿師出黎做個師傅穩袋2皮幾<br />\n不過我見勞工處請維修師傅5年經驗有A牌都係得16,17k<br />\n都唔知係咪報紙佬做新聞</blockquote><br />\n自問無乜條件咁咪做大路工<br />\n學咩人做冷門工<br />\n考警察又話唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌收撚左你先再reject offer啦"}]}